 I right in abandoning my cousin in the blackest hour of Russia'sblack history? Did I know how to exist alone in strange lands? Was thediploma I had received after being examined by a special committee (presidedby Mstislav's father, a venerable and corrupt mathematician) in all thesubjects of an ideal lyceum, which I had never attended bodily, sufficientfor Cambridge without some infernal entrance test? <9> I trudged all night,through a labyrinth of moonlight, imagining the rustlings of extincta